Use the installed Claude skill `cc-happy-resolver`.

Comment handoff contract:
- After you address an issue comment, record it with: __WORKER_DIR__/statectl.sh mark-comment <comment-id>
- After you address a review comment or review reply, record it with: __WORKER_DIR__/statectl.sh mark-sub-comment <comment-id>
- The worker adds a `hooray` reaction after the pass; comments with `hooray` are treated as read/resolved in later loops

Final output contract:
- Do not use terminal output to report the next stage
- Record the next stage with: __WORKER_DIR__/statectl.sh set-next-stage <plan|impl|review|finished>
- Call set-next-stage only at the very end of the pass, after all other statectl updates and after the branch/PR state is final
